to wake (someone up) - waka   
tomorrow - tomori
to fall - fala
many - mani
to work - woka
a lot - mani
to go - goma? mi iras al vi -> mu goma yu (fusion to avoid people to create "to come")
to come - goma?
to start - begina
to begin - begina
to try - testa
