---------

How to find a word
1) Ask people
2) Check the list
3) Try to put roots from the list together
4) Export from English

- remove h
- remove consecutive vowels (aeoiuyw)
- turn c into s or k depending on the pronunciation
- remove r if followed by consonent (does not apply for combined roots)

5) Take from other source
